name: Fake EP
description:
1. Clown
2. Come and Gone
3. 14 Straights
4. Fake
5. Place that We Call Home
6. Expendable Bored

	Despondent’s first pressed release sees them progressing into their own inimitable style of chorus-laden skate-punk. If you like your stuff fast, if you like to mosh, if you like to sing along to music, if you want to hear something new and fresh – buy this – it’s cheap!
